title: 2025 OL Connor Carty calls committing to A&M a 'dream come true' | TexAgs
text: [Texas A&M Football Recruiting](/football-recruiting) 2025 OL Connor Carty calls committing to A&M a 'dream come true' April 18, 2024 8,241 2025 Prosper offensive lineman [Connor Carty](/players/19167/connor-carty) (6-foot-5, 300 pounds) is regarded as one of the top offensive linemen in Texas, and now he is a Fightin’ Texas A&M Aggie. He knew his choice on his recent visit to Texas A&M, and after returning home, he called coach Mike Elko to deliver the news. He also spoke to TexAgs about his choice and what went into his decision. How does it feel to let everyone know you are heading to Texas A&M? Man, it’s awesome, you know. Never miss the latest news from TexAgs!
